ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 190, Saskatchewan
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 190 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN, with respect to the WILDFIRES, that affected the province, from June 6, 2015 to July 31, 2015.
